# Authors

## Creator and maintainer

**Dinesh Lakshmanan**
- GitHub: https://github.com/dinlaks
- Role: Principal architect, implementation, and validation

## Acknowledgements

This project was validated on OpenShift 4.21 with NVIDIA A30 GPUs.
It builds on the following open source projects:

- [Kueue](https://kueue.sigs.k8s.io/) — Kubernetes-native job queueing (CNCF)
- [Red Hat OpenShift AI](https://www.redhat.com/en/technologies/cloud-computing/openshift/openshift-ai) — AI/ML platform on OpenShift
- [NVIDIA GPU Operator](https://github.com/NVIDIA/gpu-operator) — GPU lifecycle management for Kubernetes
- [Red Hat Advanced Cluster Management](https://www.redhat.com/en/technologies/management/advanced-cluster-management) — Multi-cluster fleet management

## Contributing

Contributions are welcome. If you validate this on a GPU type not listed in
PREREQUISITES.md, please open a pull request updating `lib/common.sh` and
`PREREQUISITES.md` with your findings.
